<h3><li><a name="loading">LOADING JWeb</a></li></h3>
d35 14
a48 15
    <dl>
    <dt>Create a directory in desired location for <i>JWeb</i>, 
        hereafter referred to as: <i>JWEB_DIR</i> </dt>
    <dd><b>mkdir jweb; cd jweb </b></dd>   

    <p>
    <dt>LOADING FROM CDROM</dt>
    <dt> Copy files from your CDROM into: <i>JWEB_DIR</i></dt> 
    <dd><b>cp -r  "your_cdrom_device"/web/java/linux/* &nbsp; . </b></dd><p>    
    
    <dt>LOADING FROM FTP DISTRIBUTION</dt>
    <dt> unarchive files into  <i>JWEB_DIR</i></dt> 
    <dd><b>tar xvf jweb.tar</b></dd>    
    </p></dl> 
    
a49 11
